						 <p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncannyclown276" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5134477&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1556086210" alt="UncannyClown276" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5134477)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncannyclown276" >UncannyClown276</a></span> maybe 'within a radius of 5 meters' ? At that distance it's more plausible for it to manifest where it can't directly see the researcher.</p> <p>But you can do with it what you want, it's your article after all.</p> 
