					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11289142#post-4227075</guid>
				<title>radius change?</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11289142/scp-4091#post-4227075</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2019 07:34:34 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Jornax</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5264832</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It's short but sweet, and doesn't need to be any longer to tell the story it needs to tell. Well done!</p> <p>Just one thing I'm a little bit puzzled about, if the dog always appears within a 1 meter radius of junior researcher Sheperd, why would it ever need to locate them? Perhaps the radius of manifestation could be changed or the part about locating it could be left out? But that's just my 2 cents</p> <p>Upvoted anyway because I like it +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
